Before TGB was introduced, if you had a player outside of your group targeted, and were casting a 50+ group spell, the following would occur:<br>
If the player was level 30, it would not cast the spell.  It would never go past the client when it made this check.<br>
If the player was level 45, it would cast the spell, but land only on you and your party.<br>
